<SUMMARY>
SUMMARY: 

The Sanctuaries and Reserves Division of the Office of Ocean and Coastal Resource Management is soliciting proposals
for funding research within the National Estuarine Research Reserve System. The focus of funding for the upcoming
annual grant period is the restoration of estuarine and estuarine-like ecosystems. This notice sets forth funding
priorities, selection criteria, and procedures for proposal submission.



